---
import PortalLayout from '../../layouts/PortalLayout.astro'
---

<PortalLayout
  title="Advanced Diploma (Tier 2) — Sohma Institute"
  description="12-month hybrid clinical mentorship. Deep specialisation in one division with 200 hours supervised clinical practice."
>
  <article class="tier-page">

    <!-- AT A GLANCE -->
    <header class="tier-header">
      <div class="section-label">Tier 2</div>
      <h1 class="page-title">Advanced Diploma</h1>

      <div class="glance-strip">
        <div class="glance-item">
          <span class="glance-key">Duration</span>
          <span class="glance-val">12 months</span>
        </div>
        <div class="glance-divider"></div>
        <div class="glance-item">
          <span class="glance-key">Mode</span>
          <span class="glance-val">Hybrid Clinical Mentorship</span>
        </div>
        <div class="glance-divider"></div>
        <div class="glance-item">
          <span class="glance-key">Credential</span>
          <span class="glance-val">Advanced Diploma</span>
        </div>
        <div class="glance-divider"></div>
        <div class="glance-item">
          <span class="glance-key">Division</span>
          <span class="glance-val">Deep specialisation in one + cross-divisional elective</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </header>


    <!-- WHO THIS IS FOR -->
    <section class="tier-section">
      <h2>Who this is for</h2>
      <p>Practitioners who want to become competent clinical practitioners in a specific division. This is where you go from literacy to practice. You leave this tier able to assess, formulate, treat, and manage within your chosen division's therapeutic framework.</p>
    </section>


    <!-- WHAT YOU'LL LEARN -->
    <section class="tier-section">
      <h2>What you'll learn</h2>
      <p>Deep divisional specialisation. One mandatory cross-divisional elective — so a herbalist also gets exposure to systems medicine, or an entheogenic modalities student also studies somatic therapeutics. The cross-divisional requirement is a design feature. It prevents siloed thinking.</p>
      <div class="content-grid">
        <div class="content-card">
          <h3>Divisional Specialisation</h3>
          <p>Advanced clinical knowledge within your chosen division. Assessment frameworks, therapeutic protocols, case formulation at increasing complexity. The depth that Tier 1 literacy didn't provide.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="content-card">
          <h3>Cross-Divisional Elective</h3>
          <p>Mandatory exposure to one other division. This is not optional. Every practitioner trained at the Institute understands that no patient lives within a single division's framework.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="content-card">
          <h3>Clinical Hours</h3>
          <p>200 hours supervised clinical practice within Sohma House or approved partner sites. Real patient contact under mentorship — not observation, not simulation.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>


    <!-- DELIVERY -->
    <section class="tier-section">
      <h2>Delivery structure</h2>
      <div class="delivery-grid">
        <div class="delivery-block">
          <div class="delivery-tag">Asynchronous</div>
          <h3>Didactic Content</h3>
          <p>Self-paced study modules covering advanced divisional content. Completed on your own schedule. Reading, case preparation, and reflective practice.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="delivery-block">
          <div class="delivery-tag accent">Synchronous</div>
          <h3>Clinical Mentorship Rotations</h3>
          <p>Scheduled clinical mentorship within Sohma House. Supervised patient consultations, real-time clinical reasoning, peer case conferencing sessions. Every synchronous hour earns its place.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>


    <!-- ASSESSMENT -->
    <section class="tier-section">
      <h2>Assessment</h2>
      <p>Clinical portfolio. Case documentation, reflective practice records, supervisor evaluations, and peer review. No written examinations. The portfolio becomes your ongoing professional development record — it doesn't end when the credential is granted.</p>
    </section>


    <!-- PREREQUISITES -->
    <section class="tier-section">
      <h2>Prerequisites</h2>
      <p>Foundation Certificate (Tier 1) or equivalent prior learning assessment. Practitioners with substantial existing clinical experience in relevant disciplines may apply for recognition of prior learning.</p>
    </section>


    <!-- PATHWAY FORWARD -->
    <section class="tier-section">
      <h2>Pathway forward</h2>
      <div class="pathway-cards">
        <div class="pathway-card">
          <div class="pathway-icon">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="9 11 12 14 22 4"/><path d="M21 12v7a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h11"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Competent to Practise</h3>
          <p>Qualified to practise within your chosen division. This is the minimum credential for independent clinical work within the Institute's framework.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="pathway-card">
          <div class="pathway-icon">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/><path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"/><path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Associate Network Membership</h3>
          <p>Full protocol access including Tier B provisional protocols. Eligible to supervise Affiliates. Quarterly case conferencing participation.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="pathway-card">
          <div class="pathway-icon">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="12" y1="5" x2="12" y2="19"/><polyline points="19 12 12 19 5 12"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Tier 3 Entry</h3>
          <p>Completion qualifies for entry into the Graduate Diploma for cross-divisional integration and research contribution.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>


    <!-- FEES -->
    <section class="tier-section">
      <h2>Fees & funding</h2>
      <p>Tuition fees, payment plan options, and VET Student Loans eligibility details will be published prior to the first intake. Contact the Institute for current information.</p>
    </section>


    <!-- CTA -->
    <section class="tier-cta">
      <div class="cta-buttons">
        <a href="#" class="cta-primary">Apply Now</a>
        <a href="#" class="cta-secondary">Enquire</a>
        <a href="/education" class="cta-secondary">Back to all programs</a>
      </div>
    </section>

  </article>
</PortalLayout>

<style>
  .tier-page {
    font-family: 'Manrope', sans-serif; color: var(--text-heading); padding: 0 clamp(24px, 4vw, 56px);
  }
  .tier-page p { line-height: 1.8; margin: 0 0 1rem; }
  .tier-page p:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }
  .tier-page h1, .tier-page h2, .tier-page h3 { margin: 0; }
  .section-label {
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 1.25rem; font-size: 0.6875rem; font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.18em; color: var(--accent-dark); margin-bottom: 1rem; white-space: nowrap;
  }
  .section-label::after { content: ''; flex: 1; height: 1px; background: var(--accent-line); }
  .tier-header { padding: 4rem 0 2.5rem; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-light); margin-bottom: 2.5rem; }
  .page-title {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 4vw, 2.5rem);
    font-weight: 400; color: var(--text-heading); line-height: 1.15; margin-bottom: 2rem; letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }
  .glance-strip { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .glance-item { padding: 0 1.5rem; }
  .glance-item:first-child { padding-left: 0; }
  .glance-key { display: block; font-size: 0.5625rem; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.14em; color: var(--text-tertiary); margin-bottom: 0.25rem; }
  .glance-val { display: block; font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 500; color: var(--text-heading); }
  .glance-divider { width: 1px; height: 36px; background: var(--border-medium); flex-shrink: 0; }
  .tier-section { padding-bottom: 2.5rem; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--bg-card); margin-bottom: 2.5rem; }
  .tier-section h2 { font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 400; color: var(--text-heading); margin-bottom: 1.25rem; }
  .tier-section p { font-size: 0.9375rem; color: var(--text-body-70); line-height: 1.8; }
  .content-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
  .content-card { background: var(--bg-surface); border: 1px solid var(--border-light); border-radius: 6px; padding: 1.5rem; }
  .content-card h3 { font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 500; color: var(--text-heading); margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
  .content-card p { font-size: 0.8125rem; color: var(--text-body-60); line-height: 1.7; }
  .delivery-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 1rem; }
  .delivery-block { background: var(--bg-surface); border: 1px solid var(--border-light); border-radius: 6px; padding: 1.5rem; }
  .delivery-tag { display: inline-block; font-size: 0.5625rem; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: var(--text-tertiary); border: 1px solid var(--border-medium); border-radius: 2px; padding: 2px 8px; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
  .delivery-tag.accent { color: var(--accent-dark); border-color: var(--accent-border-20); }
  .delivery-block h3 { font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 500; color: var(--text-heading); margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  .delivery-block p { font-size: 0.8125rem; color: var(--text-body-60); line-height: 1.7; }
  .pathway-cards { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 1rem; }
  .pathway-card { background: var(--bg-surface); border: 1px solid var(--border-light); border-radius: 6px; padding: 1.5rem; }
  .pathway-icon { color: var(--accent-dark); opacity: 0.6; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
  .pathway-card h3 { font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 500; color: var(--text-heading); margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  .pathway-card p { font-size: 0.8125rem; color: var(--text-body-60); line-height: 1.7; }
  .tier-cta { padding: 2rem 0 4rem; }
  .cta-buttons { display: flex; gap: 0.75rem; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .cta-primary { font-size: 0.8125rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.04em; color: #fff; background: var(--accent-dark); border-radius: 4px; padding: 12px 28px; text-decoration: none; transition: background 0.2s; }
  .cta-primary:hover { background: var(--accent-darker-hover); }
  .cta-secondary { font-size: 0.8125rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--text-secondary); border: 1px solid var(--glass-12); border-radius: 4px; padding: 12px 28px; text-decoration: none; transition: border-color 0.2s, color 0.2s; }
  .cta-secondary:hover { border-color: var(--accent-border-30); color: var(--accent-dark); }
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .page-title { font-size: 1.75rem; }
    .glance-strip { flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-start; gap: 1rem; }
    .glance-divider { width: 60px; height: 1px; }
    .glance-item { padding: 0; }
    .content-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .delivery-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .pathway-cards { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }
</style>
